\f0\b 1. What exact execution workflow should Gold model?
\f1\b0 \

\f0\b Context.
\f1\b0 \'a0A strategy that consumes the official close cannot also claim a fill at that already-known close. Montauk will send a message and Max will trade manually, so the model must use a price Max could actually obtain after the signal exists.\

